===Noun===
'''context''' (''uncountable'')

# the text in which a word appears and which determines its meaning or allows its meaning to be ascertained
# the circumstances ([[background]]) or settings which determine, specify, or clarify the meaning of an event
#:''In what '''context''' did your attack on him happen? - We had a pretty tense relationship at the time, and when he insulted me I snapped.''

